milestones.description: Hamilton has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (30) in an innings in ODIs for SCOT, going past Hamilton's 12
Hamilton and Alec Davies's 61-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 2 between Hamilton and Alec Davies
Asim Butt has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for SCOT, going past Allingham
Asim Butt has conceded the most runs in an innings (55) in ODIs for SCOT, going past Nick Dyer's record of 43
Hamilton's 76 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for SCOT), surpassing Hamilton's 34
